    <edge source="Reentrancy Attack" target="Checks-Effects-Interactions Pattern">
      <data key="d6">1.0</data>
      <data key="d7">The Checks-Effects-Interactions Pattern is a recommended method to avoid Reentrancy Attacks by controlling the order of operations in smart contracts.</data>
